</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="p">;</span> &lt;&lt;&gt;&gt; DiG 9.10.6 &lt;&lt;&gt;&gt; @40.115.144.198 http418.org +tcp
